{
  "stem": "24409.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with their money, the people who were still-- add to them the people who are still in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But while I was in a-- in a central drugstore, looking for a pair of sunglasses, [INAUDIBLE] turn these things, there was a man standing next to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told me, as he was standing next to me, very inconspicuously, Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Perl.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you show yourself again in the port-- because I'd been in the port before, to find out-- in the port just once more, I guarantee you, you will be put on the next plane, and we will see to it that it's a plane which brings you back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One more move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't repeat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's all he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew I couldn't go into the port anymore, and I had to give up my plan to do something here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when I went for the Chinese visa for Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to take a ship to Mozambique.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To Lourenco Marques, which is on the other side, on the southeast side of Portugal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went with the ship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, to get this ship I needed a Portuguese exit visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I thought that I getting the permission to stay in-- to Mozambique.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was an exit visa to Mozambique, not a visa from Mozambique.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived in Mozambique, it was a very interesting trip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a freighter, which has about 20 passengers, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We landed on many small ports, Saint-Omer, and in [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Angola, in this-- so there were some other British, Portuguese colonies there, which I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
